# Automated Marketing WordPress Plugin

This plugin automates content creation and marketing efforts for your WordPress website. It fetches trending keywords, generates content, shares it on social media platforms, and adds advanced functionality like affiliate marketing, SEO optimization, email marketing, and performance analytics.

## Features

- Fetch trending keywords using a specific API
- Generate content with OpenAI GPT-3
- Share content on Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn, TikTok, and Instagram
- Automate the process using WordPress cron jobs
- Integrate affiliate marketing with automatic link insertion
- Optimize content for SEO (keyword density, meta tags, schema markup)
- Send new content to email subscribers
- Track plugin performance with analytics and reporting

## Installation

1. Upload the plugin folder to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory of your WordPress installation.
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress.
3. Configure the plugin settings in the admin panel.

## Configuration

1. Obtain API keys and access tokens for the relevant APIs (trending keywords, OpenAI, social media platforms).
2. Set up email marketing by configuring your email provider and subscriber list.
3. Configure affiliate marketing by providing a list of affiliate links and associated keywords.
4. Customize SEO optimization settings as needed.

## Usage

After configuring the plugin, the content creation and sharing process will be automated according to your settings. You can monitor the performance of your marketing efforts using the analytics and reporting features.

## Support

For any issues or feature requests, please open a GitHub issue or contact the plugin author.

